          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", daughter of the late Ken Block, according to a Racer report. She’s stepping into some awfully big shoes and all eyes will be on her, so we sincerely hope she rises to the occasion and makes her dad proud.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
